<i>Advertising young love</i>

46:06.454 --> 46:09.685
<i>For sale</i>

46:11.993 --> 46:15.793
<i>If you want to try my wares</i>

46:15.863 --> 46:20.197
<i>Come with me</i>
<i>and climb the stairs</i>

46:20.268 --> 46:23.999
<i>Love</i>

46:29.043 --> 46:34.743
<i>For sale</i>

46:36.684 --> 46:39.676
<i>She wasn't the first</i>
<i>Dahlia wanna-be I'd seen</i>

46:40.555 --> 46:42.352
<i>but she was the best.</i>

46:42.557 --> 46:44.787
<i>Was she the les</i>
<i>that Betty and Lorna knew?</i>

46:44.859 --> 46:48.124
<i>Or was she just some</i>
<i>rich bitch with a taste</i>
<i>for the low life?</i>

47:12.053 --> 47:14.146
I will not have these
in my house anymore.

47:14.222 --> 47:15.211
No!

47:15.289 --> 47:16.313
It is insane!

47:16.390 --> 47:19.154
After everything
that's happened to us, Lee.
I will nail this guy, Kay!

47:19.227 --> 47:21.457
I'll do this,
I will do this!

47:27.168 --> 47:29.693
Talk to her, Bucky.
Reason with her.

47:33.708 --> 47:34.868
Jesus.

47:37.578 --> 47:39.205
